members.name: fetchAllStatus
members.description:
Fetches the status for all agents in the DHT

You can subscribe to `knowStatus` to get updated with all the status when this call is done

Warning! Can be very slow

members.name: fetchAgentStatus
members.description: Fetches the status for the given agent

members.name: fetchAgentsStatus
members.description:
Fetches the status for the given agents in the DHT

You can subscribe to knowStatus to get updated with all the status when this call is done

Use this over `fetchAgentStatus` when fetching multiple status, as it will be more performant
